videos.headline: Ohio strikes first on Rourke QB sneak
videos.description: Nathan Rourke scores the first touchdown of the game  from one yard out in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Central Michigan gets the equalizer
videos.description: Shane Morris connects with Tyler Conklin for a 16-yard touchdown in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Ohio runs for the lead
videos.description: Nathan Rourke rushes for a 14-yard touchdown to give Ohio the lead in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Central Michigan block field goal for a TD
videos.description: Sean Bunting's 60-yard return for a touchdown on the block field goal pulls Central Michigan within 1 in the second quarter.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF (Central Michigan block field goal for a TD) 171007 ESHEET

videos.headline: Chapman's one-hander sets up Central Michigan
videos.description: Mark Chapman's one-handed catch for a 17-yard gain sets up Central Michigan with a first and goal.

videos.headline: Central Michigan retakes the lead with short TD
videos.description: Jonathan Ward scores from 1 yard  to give Central Michigan the lead.

videos.headline: Ostman's strip sack sets up the Chippewas
videos.description: Joe Ostman's force fumble of Nathan Rourke puts Central Michigan in Ohio territory.

videos.headline: Conklin's second TD catch extends the lead for the Chippewas
videos.description: Central Michigan cashes in the turnover when Shane Morris finds Tyler Conklin from 10 yards out for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Rourke's third rushing TD keeps Ohio in the fight
videos.description: Nathan Rourke scores from 4 yards out to close the deficit for Ohio in the fourth quarter.

videos.headline: Weekley and Gregory breakdown Central Michigan's 26-23 win over Ohio
videos.description: Dave Weekley and John Gregory talk about Tyler Conklin's two touchdown performance on offense and a four turnover performance on defense for Central Michigan.
